@startuml
start
fork
  :Traditional (pixel-based);
  :Read all pixel data;
  :Encode RGB values;
  :Send full frame;
  note right: High bandwidth
fork again
  :Polynomial (coefficient);
  :Extract edge contours;
  :Fit polynomials;
  :Send coefficients only;
  note right: Low bandwidth
end fork

:Compare at receiver;
:Measure quality (PSNR);
:Log bandwidth usage;
stop
@enduml
